org.aion.api.type

Class ContractAbiEntry

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.aion.api.type.ContractAbiEntry

  • public final class ContractAbiEntry
extends java.lang.Object
    Represents an internal representation of a single entry in the JSON ABI Contains all relevant information pertaining to that entry. Typically the API does not require the manual creation of such a class, instead it is returned by IContract or compile related API.
    Author:
    Jay Tseng
